<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;SPAULDING REHABILITATION HOSPITAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Spaulding Rehabilitation Hospital is a 132-bed rehabilitation teaching hospital located in Boston, Massachusetts, and is the official teaching hospital for Harvard Medical School’s Department of Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Spaulding Rehabilitation Hospital is a hospital where Ross Zafonte works, focusing on physical medicine and rehabilitation."</data>
