  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Magee Rehabilitation Hospital is a 96-bed specialty medical rehabilitation hospital located in Center City Philadelphia, offering various rehabilitation services."&lt;SEP&gt;"Magee Rehabilitation Hospital, founded in 1958, is a 96-bed specialty medical rehabilitation hospital providing physical and cognitive rehabilitation services."</data>
