</node>
<node id="&quot;STEROID&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Steroid is a type of chemical compound, specifically Prasterone, which is used as a supplement and medication."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fbc2b7131aa3feb06fb971135b45d0d0</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ANDROSTANE DERIVATIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Androstane derivative is a specific type of steroid, such as Prasterone, which is used as a supplement and medication."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fbc2b7131aa3feb06fb971135b45d0d0</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TESTOSTERONE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Testosterone is a hormone from which 3α,5β-Androstanediol is formed as a metabolite."&lt;SEP&gt;"Testosterone is a hormone that can be administered through various methods such as gel, patch, injection, tablet, or oral intake, often discussed in the context of its benefits or harms for aging individuals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Testosterone is a hormone that can be used as a performance-enhancing drug in sports, leading to bans for athletes who test positive for it."&lt;SEP&gt;"Testosterone is a male hormone that continues to be produced in limited quantities after Zeuterin treatment, returning to normal levels after two years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Testosterone is a medication and naturally occurring steroid hormone used to treat male hypogonadism and certain types of breast cancer, and may also be used to increase athletic ability through doping."&lt;SEP&gt;"Testosterone is a steroid hormone derived from Prasterone, which is used as a supplement and medication."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-638820e59bfb7b6ae71fb76f6c2e0231&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88c6ddddf1f8c80a543edcbb6c4d141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae275111e6571cf6c99a417caff5d8e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fbc2b7131aa3feb06fb971135b45d0d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-187952f0ca3db764130690974a785cd6</data>
</node>
