  <data key="d1">"Zinc Gluconate is an ingredient in Zeuterin that destroys sperm and causes inflammation, leading to fibrosis and sterility."&lt;SEP&gt;"Zinc Gluconate is an ingredient in Zeuterin that destroys sperm and causes inflammation, leading to sterility."&lt;SEP&gt;"Zinc Gluconate is an ingredient in Zeuterin, an injectable product used for certain medical purposes."</data>
