  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TESTICLES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Testicles are the specific organs within the dogs targeted by the Zeuterin treatment to achieve sterilization."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SPERM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sperm is the target of the Zeuterin treatment, which destroys it to prevent reproduction."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INFLAMMATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Inflammation is a result of the Zeuterin treatment, leading to fibrosis and sterility."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FIBROSIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fibrosis is a consequence of the Zeuterin treatment, contributing to sterility."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;STERILITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sterility is the primary outcome of the Zeuterin treatment, preventing the production of viable sperm."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-da47f7fbfeff85b3d6a1641e3bae39b1</data>
</node>
